<view class="page-shell--plain login-page">
  <view class="login-hero">
    <view class="login-logo">即</view>
    <view class="page-title">登录即出</view>
    <view class="page-subtitle">登录后可以发布闲置、收藏商品并联系卖家</view>
  </view>

  <view class="surface-card login-card">
    <view wx:if="{{authStatus === 'authenticated' && user}}" class="logged-in-panel">
      <view class="logged-avatar">{{user.avatarText}}</view>
      <view class="logged-copy">
        <text class="logged-title">当前已登录</text>
        <text class="logged-name">{{user.nickname}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view wx:else>
      <view class="login-purpose-title">使用微信身份安全登录</view>
      <view class="purpose-list">
        <view class="purpose-item">
          <view class="purpose-mark">1</view>
          <text>云端识别当前微信身份，不在页面展示身份标识</text>
        </view>
        <view class="purpose-item">
          <view class="purpose-mark">2</view>
          <text>首次登录创建最小用户记录，再次进入恢复同一用户</text>
        </view>
        <view class="purpose-item">
          <view class="purpose-mark">3</view>
          <text>不会自动获取你的微信昵称、头像、手机号或学校信息</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>

    <view wx:if="{{errorMessage}}" class="login-error">
      <text>{{errorMessage}}</text>
      <text
        wx:if="{{authStatus === 'error'}}"
        class="retry-link"
        bindtap="onRetryRestore"
      >
        重新校验
      </text>
    </view>

    <button
      wx:if="{{authStatus !== 'authenticated'}}"
      class="wechat-login-button"
      loading="{{isLoggingIn}}"
      disabled="{{isLoggingIn || isReturning}}"
      bindtap="onLoginTap"
    >
      {{isLoggingIn ? '正在登录' : '微信身份登录'}}
    </button>

    <button
      wx:else
      class="wechat-login-button"
      disabled="{{isReturning}}"
      bindtap="continueAfterLogin"
    >
      {{isReturning ? '正在返回' : '继续'}}
    </button>

    <button class="back-button" bindtap="onBackTap">暂不登录，返回浏览</button>
  </view>

  <view class="privacy-note">
    登录仅用于确认账号身份和恢复本地会话摘要。项目不会缓存微信身份标识、访问令牌或微信密钥。
  </view>
</view>
